{"tid":1180210,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"其實火箭呢隊波係唔係已經頂, 迪帥已經技窮","createTime":"2019-05-31T16:03:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-01T05:56:21.000Z","uid":155883,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"fd0e566b8d66d8aa6901f0fbdbb7fc15adc8fb9d","tid":1180210,"uid":155883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T16:03:34.000Z","msg":"迪帥已經冇貨<br />\n今年咁好機會都把握唔到, 上年就話傷CP3<br />\n但事實佢對面都傷左個FMVP, GAME 7 炒20幾球3分<br />\n再講, GAME3 大家FULL TEAM講緊輸40分<br />\n就好明顯見到兩隊差距<br />\n今年, KD傷GAME6, CURRY 半場零分<br />\n對面再讓多個表弟, 但都係輸波, 仲有咩說話講<br />\n迪帥係有料既, 早係太陽時期即使贏唔到冠軍<br />\n都起碼入下FINALS 啦<br />\n但咁多季都係西決止步<br />\n大家仲記唔記得2017 對馬剌, JH比人搶左MVP果年<br />\nGAME6 KW傷左, 但最後馬剌都贏左入西決<br />\n火箭真係浪費左好多機會<br />\nCP3終身無冠"},{"pid":"dbfc32e3efe814d9de1d82266341f91f8b66ec12","tid":1180210,"uid":155883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T16:04:14.000Z","msg":"火箭唔知點番本, CP3 1.6億都照簽<br />\n唉"},{"pid":"9e0b182be763350945815146ee50a48fac815227","tid":1180210,"uid":155883,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T01:10:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d91f9ae376331f98be91aa3d9e678a53c7389aeb","tid":1180210,"uid":30040,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T01:47:47.000Z","msg":"當時話用1.6億簽cp3 件玻璃老嘢果時已經話玩完，火箭區D人仲話你識咩呀屌番我轉頭，之後冇再入過箭區了 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e4a9a92f94d1651e79c642c12f13ba6b357323d","tid":1180210,"uid":87155,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T01:55:05.000Z","msg":"火賤狗係最撚低賤 屌你老未 搞到玩具撚比人笑"},{"pid":"0142cfa6dd5200be03570b2905f7d02952a7484b","tid":1180210,"uid":138578,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T01:55:19.000Z","msg":"今年明顯弱過上年啦 由常規賽開季就咁差 係JH一個打返上黎"},{"pid":"7002fa495f79c7f369afd4217b64d59dc415f879","tid":1180210,"uid":155883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0142cfa6dd5200be03570b2905f7d02952a7484b","tid":1180210,"uid":138578,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":